Hadfield and Mrs. Theodore Schlegel, chairs of the mother-daughter debutante 
announcement luncheon. MARIANNA DIAMOS; Photo, Joseph Pinola, left, chats with 
Carolyn and William Carter, outgoing chairman of the Music Center fund-raising 
effort. JAN SONNENMAIR; Photo, Mrs. Stephen Stiles, chair of this year's Monte 
Carlo Ball. 
</P>
