<P>
Photo, Sarah, 7, who is paralyzed and breathes on ventilator, pets dog at 
Downey hospital. She has lived in hospitals since she was 2 months old. Foster 
family wants to adopt her but can't find nursing care at Medi-Cal rates. AXEL 
KOESTER 
</P>
