<SECTION>
<P>
Book Review; Page 3; Book Review Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Edvard Munch, "Puberty," 1895. From "The History of Modern Painting: 
Matisse, Munch and Rouault" (Albert Skira, Geneva). 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA082089-0109 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 97033 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 20, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
