<TEXT>
<P>
Ronald L. Budman has been appointed executive vice president and chief 
financial officer at Childrens Hospital of Orange County. Budman, 53, replaces 
Thomas P. Jones., who was promoted to president and chief executive officer of 
the 202-bed pediatric facility in Orange. Budman was recruited from Downey 
Community Hospital where he was vice president of finance. 
